IMPORTANT: Inside the JSON strings, you MUST escape backslashes (e.g. use "\\cite{...}" instead of "\cite{...}").
Format:
```json
[
  {
    "file": "relative/path/to/file.tex",
    "line": 123,
    "description": "Description of the issue",
    "severity": "critical|major|minor",
    "suggested_fix": "Exact string to replace or description of change"
  }
]
```
